<note n="0892003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0892003">應＋（下）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0892004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0892004">也＝耶【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0892005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0892005">耶＝也【聖】＊</note>
<note n="0892006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0892006">〔也〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0892007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0892007">〔棄竟〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0892008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0892008">生＝世【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0893001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893001">〔若本…漏〕二十九字－【聖】</note>
<note n="0893002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893002">〔現在前〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0893003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893003">〔若本…禪〕二十六字－【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0893004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893004">〔修〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0893005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893005">（或）＋護【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0893006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893006">〔味餘〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0893007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893007">上＋（無因）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0893008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893008">應＋（下一）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0893009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893009">〔次第…餘〕十四字－【宮】</note>
<note n="0893010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893010">無漏＋（下）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0893011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893011">〔阿毘曇〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0893012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893012">跋渠第二竟＝品第三十五竟【聖】</note>
<note n="0893013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893013">〔秦一…言〕九字－【三】【宮】，〔秦〕－【聖】</note>
<note n="0893014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893014">此下聖本有光明皇后願文</note>
<note n="0893015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893015">〔八犍度〕－【宋】【元】【宮】，八犍度論＝經【聖】</note>
<note n="0893016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0893016">第二十六＋（定犍度第七之二）【宋】【元】</note>
</p>
